        <div class="section section_with_padding section_color" id="research"> 
            <h2 class="section_color6">Research Interest</h2>
            My main research interest is in Natural Language Processing and its application in education. I am also interested in Text Mining and Spoken Dialogue Systems.
			My current Research focus is on Automatic Essay Assessment which is about using Natural Language Processing for Assessing Students' Writing Ability at Scale.
            
